	" is a space flight shooter game that was originally developed for MS-DOS and later received ports to many systems such as the SNES, Sega CD, and PlayStation. In this game, you are an upstart soldier in the war between the Terrans and the Kilrathi, which are feline bipedal aliens whose social values are very incompatible with humanity's. Take command of a ship and complete missions that will either lead you to eventual victory or failure, depending on how you play.
